{
  "texts": [
    "Deep CNNs can be built using the backpropagation technique to perform tasks such as classifying handwritten digits.",
    "Deep CNNs have dominated various computer vision and image processing applications, and recent applications of CNNs for time series prediction have generated highly promising results 70, 71.",
    "Convolution, pooling layer, and fully connected layers are the main building blocks that CNN's use to perform spatial hierarchies of features.",
    "The deep CNN model is mostly well adopted with time series signals for various regression and classification problems as introduced in 72.",
    "The CNN models perform the optimization performance with less memory consumption, there is already a connection between the neurons in the adjacent layer of the fully connected networks."
  ]
}